2. Upon tapping on the button, navigate to a new view containing a segmented control with options for different story genres.
3. When a genre is selected, navigate to a new view containing options for characters, settings, and the option to include conflict or plot.
4. When the user has made their selections, async/await call the openAI chat GPT API with the user's choices as input.
